messages.messageBody:
Sandra

I was more wanting to understand if there was a place you go, or game
you play or some kind of strategy other than buying them. I guess just
wondering is there something you have to do to get them. I have the
same trouble with the dabloons, and nerkmid coins etc. I just don't
understand it all yet. We have only been playing for a few months.
Since Aug/Sept I think. Maybe these are just things you learn in time
from playing and looking around. Thanks!

Dana
